data.description: Create unforgettable memories in this stunning KB Home in Sunset Grove, boasting a beautiful brick front and an open great room. Entertain your guests in the spacious kitchen, fully equipped with laminate countertops, stainless steel appliances, and 30-in. cabinets. Take a well-deserved break in the primary suite, featuring an extended vanity and a tub with a Moen Chateau® WaterSense showerhead. Additional home features include a fully equipped security system, full gutters, and automatic sprinklers. Sunset Grove offers a park, playground, and covered pavilion for residents. Situated between I-45 and Hwy 6, residents take advantage of easy access to Galveston and Downtown Houston. Popular dining, shopping, and entertainment can be found at the nearby Tanger® Outlets and Baybrook Mall. Zoned to Hitchcock ISD.
